column5: Need three others,gonna talk to a bud shortly and see.I be heading out from the hammer, Anyone interested?
If it wasnt for the Maiden show that day I would probably jump in on this but I usually go down eary and beat the Smoke shoreline for toothy telephone poles.  Thanks for the offer Peter
Your first in line,for cancellations,still waiting for fishhunter to reply back.We all may be out of luck!
